A '''development easement''' is a [[legal agreement]] by which a [[landowner]] surrenders the right to develop a designated parcel of [[property]]. Some [[local government|local]] and [[state government]]s have programs to acquire development easements from private landowners to prevent conversion of [[Arable land|farmland]] to other uses.

